params.name: data.page_size
params.description: The requested page size. Server might return fewer results than requested. If unspecified, returns at most 100 SKUs. The maximum value is 1000; the server will coerce values above 1000. Optional.

params.description: A token for a page of results other than the first page. Optional.

params.name: data.auth_token
params.description: The super admin of the resold customer generates this token to authorize a reseller to access their Cloud Identity and purchase entitlements on their behalf. You can omit this token after authorization. See https://support.google.com/a/answer/7643790 for more details.

params.name: data.language_code
params.description: The BCP-47 language code. For example, "en-US". The response will localize in the corresponding language code, if specified. The default value is "en-US". Optional.
